Saepe illam perhibent ardenti corde furentem clarisonas imo fudisse e pectore voceS,

ac tum praeruptos tristem conscendere montes, unde aciem in pelagi vastos protenderet aestus, tum tremuli salis adversas procurrere in undas mollia nudatae tollentem tegmina surae,
